<p class="ql-align-justify">松下碧水边</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">晨起听鸟鸣</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">晚卧观云卷</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">是非一壶酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一醉便是仙</p>
