<p class="ql-align-justify">幼居寒舍今犹在</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">人去屋空四壁凉</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">街边顽童不相识</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">笑问尔是谁家郎</p>
